I see that you have proved you skill against the Champion, Stone Fists. Well done. I hereby grant you the title, Champion of Stone.
I see that you have proved you skill against the Champion, Azaxis. Well done. I hereby grant you the title, Champion of Sickles.
I see that you have proved you skill against the Champion, Killagurg. Well done. I hereby grant you the title, Champion of the Wild.
I see that you have proved you skill against the Champion, the Demon Swarm Matron. Well done. I hereby grant you the title, Champion of the Hive.
I see that you have proved you skill against our mysterious Champion, The Master. Well done. I hereby grant you the title, Champion of Assassins.
I see that you have proved you skill against the Champion, Gladiator Diemos. Well done indeed. I hereby grant you the title, Immortal Champion.

In addition to your new title and this useful hook caster, I'll also give you a token that you can trade back to me for a great deal of practical knowledge, or you can trade it in to Fiun Rehlyun at the Fiun settlement in the Halaetan Isles for a blank Augmentation gem. A difficult decision, I know.
I see that you have proven yourself against the Pumpkin King. Well done.
Since you have slain him, you must be will be known as the "Pumpkin Throne Usurper."
Oh, and we found this mixed up in the mess you left in his arena.
And I believe you have earned this bit of practical knowledge.
The Arbitrator reaches out and lightly touches your forehead, sending a jolt of new understanding through you mind.
I see that you have proved you skill against the Thunder Chicken. Well done.
You shall be known to all as the "Thunder Chicken Slayer".
I see that you have proved your skill against the Very Mad Cow. Well done.
You shall be known to all as the "Mad Cow Slayer".
